				<div class="brokenheartBackground m-auto">
					<div class="brokenheartHeart"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- Row 2 -->
		<div class="row align-items-center py-4">
			<div class="col-md-6 order-md-12">
					<h3 class="bold">Creative Machines</h3>
					<p>At VRG, we are less creative machines, and more creative producers of machinations, but in the nicest possible sense.</p>
					<p> We scheme and conspire together, to design and devise intriguing strategies for our clients, and ultimately for their global user base. We <span class="italic">love</span> what we do!</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
				<div class="m-auto creativemachinesBackground">
					<div class="creativemachinesPulley1 animated rotateCW"></div>
					<div class="creativemachinesPulley2 animated rotateCW"></div>
					<div class="bubbles">
						<div class="bubble"></div>
						<div class="bubble"></div>
						<div class="bubble"></div>
						<div class="bubble"></div>
						<div class="bubble"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- Row 3 -->
		<div class="row align-items-center py-4">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h3 class="bold">Storytellers</h3>
				<p>Each story becomes a part of history. VRG's creations each tell a story of art borne from need, climaxing with flair and imagining.</p>
				<p>Our client accolades and user experiences spur us on to even greater and higher plains of conceptual form. Let our next story become a part of your history.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<div class="brokenheartBackground m-auto">
					<div class="brokenheartHeart"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

